  <summary date="2021-12-15T18:45:18Z" status="Introduced in House">Gun Theft Prevention Act

This bill makes various changes to federal firearms laws related to detecting and deterring the theft of firearms from federally licensed gun dealers.

Among the changes, the bill establishes security requirements for gun dealers; background check requirements for employees of gun dealers; inspection requirements for the Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms and Explosives; and reporting requirements for individual gun owners.</summary>
